{"prompt": "Design a modern corporate site for a biotech startup. The aesthetic should incorporate a bright cyan blue.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>BioNova Innovations</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #00BCD4; /* Bright Cyan Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #E0F7FA; /* Lighter Cyan */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --footer-color: #f5f5f5;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1.5rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #0097A7;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #FFFFFF;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            border-color: white;\n        }\n\n        .about-content, .services-content, .contact-content {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .about-text, .services-item, .contact-form {\n            flex-basis: 45%;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about-text p, .services-item p {\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .services-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n        }\n\n        .services-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 0.8rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #0097A7;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            .about-content, .services-content, .contact-content {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .about-text, .services-item, .contact-form {\n                flex-basis: 100%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 0.5rem 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>BioNova Innovations</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Our Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Transforming Tomorrow Through Biotechnology</h2>\n            <p>Pioneering research and development to create groundbreaking solutions for a healthier future.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"btn\">Get In Touch</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <div class=\"about-content\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <p>BioNova Innovations is a forward-thinking biotech startup dedicated to advancing human health and well-being. Our team of passionate scientists and innovators leverages cutting-edge technology and rigorous research to develop novel therapeutic solutions and diagnostic tools.</p>\n                <p>We believe in the power of science to solve complex challenges, and we are committed to making a tangible impact on people's lives through ethical practices and scientific excellence.</p>\n            </div>\n            <!-- Placeholder for an image or graphic -->\n            <div style=\"flex-basis: 45%; text-align: center;\">\n                <svg width=\"150\" height=\"150\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"color: var(--primary-color);\">\n                    <path d=\"M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.411 0-8-3.589-8-8s3.589-8 8-8 8 3.589 8 8-3.589 8-8 8zm1-9h-2v2h2v-2zm0 4h-2v2h2v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"/>\n                </svg>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"services-content\">\n            <div class=\"services-item\">\n                <h3>Drug Discovery</h3>\n                <p>Accelerating the identification and development of novel drug candidates for unmet medical needs.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"services-item\">\n                <h3>Gene Therapy</h3>\n                <p>Exploring advanced gene editing technologies for treating genetic disorders.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"services-item\">\n                <h3>Biomarker Development</h3>\n                <p>Creating innovative diagnostic tools for early disease detection and personalized medicine.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"services-item\">\n                <h3>Bioprocessing</h3>\n                <p>Optimizing manufacturing processes for biologics and advanced therapies.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-content\">\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n            <!-- Placeholder for contact info -->\n            <div style=\"flex-basis: 45%; text-align: left;\">\n                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@bionovainnovations.com</p>\n                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (123) 456-7890</p>\n                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Innovation Drive, Biotech City, CA 90210</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 BioNova Innovations. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}